'We denied access to every Real Housewife who applied,' said Tim Geary, the LA branch's former director of membership. 'Kim Kardashian has unsuccessfully tried numerous times.'

'Kobe Bryant showed up and chose not to join. We didn't let him up,' he added. 'There was a debate over Britney Spears. Not sure how that played out.'

The super-exclusive clique on 9200 Sunset Boulevard, now celebrating its fifth birthday, is the third such outpost, following its sister spots in London and New York. 

